episodes.title: RISE TV HIS LAST INTERVIEW ON EARTH | ESCAPING SCIENTOLOGY | DOUG SCOTT KRAMER (Legacy Episode)
episodes.description:
Doug Scott Kramer has a channel that takes the viewer on a very personal and intimate journey of what it was like being raised in the Scientology cult - from his father first becoming indoctrinated into it when I was a child, to his own decades-long career as a card-carrying Manchurian Candidate Scientologist - through to his subsequent wake up, escape, and on-going healing process.
